snippet.title: Might & Magic Heroes Online: Official Launch Trailer [INT]
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/your_journey_starts_here

For the first time ever the classic gameplay of a Heroes game has been combined with MMORPG elements. Play an epic adventure together with friends and become the true hero of Ashan!
